data.description: Back on the market! No fault of the seller. Incredible opportunity to check out this custom built home that has so many wonderful features. This home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with a large 2.5garage. Upgraded features throughout home: 10ft ceilings!!!, trey ceiling, split floor pan, 2 living areas, tile throughout main living, new carpet inbedrooms, spacious kitchen with granite countertops, including a kitchen island, fireplace, jetted tub, separate shower, shower niches and more!!! Thebackyard offers terraced surfaces and open areas for entertaining and a storage shed. No HOA! You cannot miss out on this one!
